        p
            | The 
            code.highlighter-rouge text-hide()
            |  class and mixin has been deprecated as of v4.1. It will be removed entirely in v5.
    p
        | Utilize the 
        code.highlighter-rouge .text-hide
        |  class or mixin to help replace an elementâ€™s text content with a background image.
    figure.highlight
        pre
            code.css
                | h1.text-hide Custom heading
    figure.highlight
        pre
            code.scss
                | // Usage as a mixin
                | .heading {
                |     @include text-hide;
                | }
    p
        | Use the 
        code.highlighter-rouge .text-hide
        |  class to maintain the accessibility and SEO benefits of heading tags, but want to utilize a 
        code.highlighter-rouge background-image
        |  instead of text.
